# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CloudVitta Frontend — environment template
# Copy to `frontend/.env` only if you need to override defaults.
# Vite exposes vars prefixed with VITE_ to the browser, so NEVER
# put secrets here.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Backend API origin (scheme + host, NO trailing /api — the client appends it).
# Leave UNSET for local dev: requests fall back to `/api` via the Vite dev proxy
# (see vite.config.js). Set it in production (Netlify) to the backend origin:
# VITE_API_URL="https://api.cloudvitta.in"
